Lesson 1.5 - know thy time

---------- [L1]

RSS feed link: https://rss.com/podcasts/footnerdprogram/412301/

Video link: https://youtu.be/tYsB4PoZV9s

Creators: Malin & Ruth

Framework (draft only, to be modified by teachers):

- Time as our only scarce resource
- Time audit
- Shortcomings of our memory
- Alignment check
- System: time block calendar
- Schedule what matters


Audio lesson notes:
- detailed notes and timestamps from the audio lesson [to be added in future]


Experiments (nano to macro)
- Do a 7-day real time audit. Account for each hour of your day real time - even if it's inconvenient (record each day for a week)
- How much time do you think you spend on social media per week? Track and verify for 7 days
- Write down the top 3 things worth your time
- What are your most productive times of the day?
- Create a time block calendar for a week


